<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Freedom AI Hub | المنصة العالمية لإدارة المتاجر</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif; background: #020617; color: #f8fafc; overflow-x: hidden; }
        .glass { background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
        .gold-gradient { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ca8a04 0%, #eab308 100%); }
        .text-gradient { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fbbf24, #d97706); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .card-hover:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: #eab308; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen">

    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 p-4">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto glass rounded-2xl p-4 flex justify-between items-center border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 gold-gradient rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-yellow-500/20">
                    <span class="text-black font-black text-xl italic">F</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter">FREEDOM <span class="text-yellow-500">AI</span></h1>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 font-bold text-sm">
                <a href="#" class="text-yellow-500">الرئيسية</a>
                <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition">المتاجر المتصلة</a>
                <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition">التقارير الذكية</a>
            </div>
            <button class="bg-white text-black px-5 py-2 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm hover:bg-yellow-500 transition shadow-xl">لوحة التحكم</button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 grid lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        
        <aside class="lg:col-span-1 space-y-6">
            <div class="glass p-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 shadow-2xl">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-yellow-500 text-2xl">⚙️</span> إعدادات الربط الشامل
                </h3>
                
                <div class="space-y-5">
                    <div>
                        <label class="text-xs text-gray-500 block mb-2 px-1 text-right">منصة المتجر</label>
                        <select id="storePlatform" class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-3 rounded-xl outline-none focus:border-yellow-500 text-sm transition-all appearance-none">
                            <option value="shopify">Shopify - شوبيفاي</option>
                            <option value="salla">Salla - سلة</option>
                            <option value="zid">Zid - زيد</option>
                            <option value="woocommerce">WooCommerce - ووكومرس</option>
                            <option value="amazon">Amazon - أمازون</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="text-xs text-gray-500 block mb-2 px-1 text-right">رابط المتجر (Domain)</label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="freedom-store.com" class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-3 rounded-xl text-sm outline-none focus:border-yellow-500">
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label class="text-xs text-gray-500 block mb-2 px-1 text-right">مفتاح الوصول (API Key)</label>
                        <input type="password" placeholder="••••••••••••••••••••" class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-3 rounded-xl text-sm outline-none focus:border-yellow-500">
                    </div>

                    <button class="w-full gold-gradient text-black py-4 rounded-xl font-black shadow-lg shadow-yellow-600/10 hover:scale-[1.02] transition transform active:scale-95">
                        حفظ بيانات المتجر
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="glass p-5 rounded-3xl border-r-4 border-yellow-500 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">AI Status</p>
                    <p class="text-sm font-black">Freedom Core v3.0</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse shadow-lg shadow-green-500/50"></div>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-8">
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[3rem] relative overflow-hidden border border-white/5">
                <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>

                <div class="relative z-10 mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">أهلاً بك يا <span class="text-gradient underline decoration-yellow-500/20">إمبراطور</span></h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        هذه المنصة صُممت خصيصاً لتختصر عليك ساعات من العمل. ارفع صور منتجاتك الآن، واترك الباقي لذكاء Freedom الاصطناعي ليقوم بالتحليل، التسعير، والنشر.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-600 to-yellow-400 rounded-[2.5rem] blur opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition duration-1000"></div>
                    <div id="uploadZone" class="relative bg-slate-900/50 border-2 border-dashed border-slate-700 rounded-[2.5rem] p-16 text-center hover:border-yellow-500 transition-all cursor-pointer">
                        <div class="text-7xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">🖼️</div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-2">ارفع صور منتجاتك هنا</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">سيقوم النظام تلقائياً بتحديد المتجر النشط وبدء عملية النشر الذكي.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10">
                    <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 card-hover shadow-xl">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">✍️</div>
                        <h4 class="font-black text-yellow-500 mb-2 italic text-sm underline decoration-yellow-500/30">SEO Content</h4>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 leading-tight">كتابة وصف منتج جذاب ومتوافق مع محركات البحث بجميع اللغات.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 card-hover shadow-xl">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">📊</div>
                        <h4 class="font-black text-yellow-500 mb-2 italic text-sm underline decoration-yellow-500/30">Market Analysis</h4>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 leading-tight">تحليل الأسعار في المتاجر المنافسة واقتراح السعر الأمثل للربح.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 card-hover shadow-xl">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🌍</div>
                        <h4 class="font-black text-yellow-500 mb-2 italic text-sm underline decoration-yellow-500/30">Auto Publish</h4>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 leading-tight">ضغطة واحدة تكفي لنشر المنتج في جميع متاجر العميل في آن واحد.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button class="w-full mt-10 bg-white text-black font-black py-6 rounded-[1.5rem] text-xl shadow-2xl hover:bg-yellow-500 transition-all transform active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                    🚀 ابدأ عملية النشر الشامل
                </button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-10 px-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 text-gray-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
        <p>© 2026 Freedom AI Enterprise - Luxury Commerce Solutions</p>
        <div class="flex gap-8">
            <span class="hover:text-yellow-500 cursor-pointer">Security</span>
            <span class="hover:text-yellow-500 cursor-pointer">API Docs</span>
            <span class="hover:text-yellow-500 cursor-pointer">Contact</span>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
